<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٦٤٨١ - هُشَيْمٌ، عَنِ الْحَسَنِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«حَرُمَتْ عَلَيْهِ، فَلْيَسْتَأْنِفْ نِكَاحَهَا إِنْ أَرَادَهَا»</span> حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٦٤٨٢ - هُشَيْمٌ، عَنْ حَجَّاجٍ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَقَالَ ذَلِكَ الشَّعْبِيُّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>